Privacy Policy

Last updated: 31-08-2024

1. Introduction

Welcome to UpDownWordle! Your privacy is important to us, and we are committed to protecting it. This Privacy Policy explains how we handle your information when you use our game.

2. Information We Collect

While UpDownWordle does not collect personal information directly, the services we integrate with may collect certain data:

  - Google AdMob: We use Google AdMob to display advertisements within the game. Google AdMob may collect certain information, including device identifiers, location data, and other relevant data, to provide personalized ads. Please refer to Google's Privacy Policy for more information on how your data is handled by Google AdMob.

  - Google Play Store: We connect with the Google Play Store to allow players to make donations. Any personal or payment information you provide through the Google Play Store is subject to Google's policies. For more details, please review the Google Play Privacy Policy.

3. How We Use Your Information

  - Advertisements: The data collected by Google AdMob is used to deliver personalized advertisements within the game. We do not have access to this data, and it is managed solely by Google.

  - Donations: Any donations made through the Google Play Store are processed and managed by Google. We do not collect or store any payment information.

4. Third-Party Services

As mentioned, our game connects with third-party services (Google AdMob and Google Play Store) for advertisements and donations. These services may collect and use data in accordance with their own privacy policies. We encourage you to review these policies to understand how your information is handled by these services.

5. Childrenâ€™s Privacy

UpDownWordle is suitable for players of all ages. However, when using third-party services like Google AdMob and the Google Play Store, data may be collected from users, including children under 13. We encourage parents and guardians to monitor their children's use of the game and guide them in understanding how their information might be used by third-party services.

6. Changes to This Privacy Policy

We may update our Privacy Policy from time to time. Any changes will be posted on this page with a new "Last updated" date. Please check this page periodically for updates.
